---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure | Obsidian Plugins Guide" description="Affiliate disclosure for Obsidian Plugins Guide." canonicalURL="https://notes-automate.com/affiliate-disclosure/">
  <article class="policy-page">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="lead">We want readers to know exactly how this site may earn money and how that affects editorial choices.</p>
    <h2>Short version</h2>
    <p>Some links on Obsidian Plugins Guide may be affiliate links. If you click one and buy a product or service, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.</p>
    <h2>How affiliate links are used</h2>
    <p>Affiliate links help pay for hosting, research time, testing accounts, writing, editing, and maintenance. They do not buy placement in our rankings, and they do not guarantee a positive recommendation. When a product has meaningful drawbacks, we describe them even if an affiliate program exists.</p>
    <h2>What we do not do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We do not accept payment to hide cons or inflate ratings.</li>
      <li>We do not let vendors rewrite our conclusions.</li>
      <li>We do not recommend products solely because they pay commissions.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Reader responsibility</h2>
    <p>Prices, features, availability, and policies can change. Always check the vendor's official page before purchasing, especially for subscription software, physical equipment, warranties, data privacy, and refund terms.</p>
    <h2>Questions</h2>
    <p>Send affiliate disclosure questions or correction requests to <a href="mailto:hello@notes-automate.com">hello@notes-automate.com</a>.</p>
    <p>Last updated: May 10, 2026.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .policy-page h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
  .policy-page .lead { color: #4b5563; font-size: 1.08rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .policy-page h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 2rem 0 .75rem; }
  .policy-page ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  .policy-page li { margin-bottom: .55rem; }
  .policy-page a { color: var(--accent, #2563eb); text-decoration: underline; }
</style>

